{"about_the_game":"Song of a Spirit is a Game Jam submission made in 14 days. It is a crafting game that explores an unconstrained approach to writing tunes, rhythms and melodies. <br><br>Gameplay:<br>Layout your note orbs in a classic linear or randomly placed fashion. Use the stone plated as timing indicators, place a pair of trigger totems in any orientation and launch an energy wave to trigger your note orbs from any direction. <br><br>Mechanics<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tone Wand <br></li><li> 10 Sounds (4 Percussive &amp; 6 Tonal) to experiment with<br></li><li> Tone wand to Set, Retrieve, Trigger the Note orbs<br></li><li> Trigger Totems for triggering Note Orbs from any direction<br></li><li> Routing and trigger poles for connecting, routing and looping the music patterns</li></ul><br>Use sound and resources of the surrounding environment to craft various whimsical instruments.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1697847766","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111130/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1697847766","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111130/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1697847766","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111130/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1697847766","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Song of a Spirit is a Game Jam submission made in 14 days. It is a crafting game that explores an unconstrained approach to writing tunes, rhythms and melodies. <br><br>Gameplay:<br>Layout your note orbs in a classic linear or randomly placed fashion. Use the stone plated as timing indicators, place a pair of trigger totems in any orientation and launch an energy wave to trigger your note orbs from any direction. <br><b